                    <h2 style="font-weight: 600">WHAT IS AN MUN?</h2>
                    <br/>
                    <p>The Model United Nations Conference is a simulation of the United Nations. With an insight into currently significant issues, MUNs are the best tools in the making of a globally aware citizen where delegates discuss, deliberate and tackle various matters of concern with effective knowledge in a nuanced and diplomatic manner. It gives the delegates a chance to hone their skills by bringing together varied facets including public speaking, research and critical analysis. Delegations like these are platforms to inspire the youth to think outside the box. </p>
                    <p class="text-center show-more show-more-1" onclick="showMoreText('1')">Show more <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></p>
                    <p class="hidden-text-1">“The Charter of the United Nations expresses the noblest aspirations of man: abjuration of force in the settlement of disputes between states; the assurance of human rights and fundamental freedoms for all without distinction as to race, sex, language or religion; the safeguarding of international peace and security.” - Haile Selassie</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h2 style="font-weight: 600">ABOUT CHITKARA UNIVERSITY AND CHITKARA UNIVERSITY MUNSOC:</h2>
                    <br/>
                    <p>Chitkara University has been established by and managed by passionate academicians with the sole mission of holistic growth of each student. </p>
                    <p>It is run with the vision “To be a globally recognized organization promoting academic excellence through interdisciplinary applied research and to expand realms of knowledge through innovation.”</p>
                    <p class="text-center show-more show-more-2" onclick="showMoreText('2')">Show more <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></p>
                    <p class="hidden-text-2">Chitkara University MUNSOC was established in the year 2010 with an aim of acquainting the future leaders of society with various skills that are essential in the making of a responsible citizen. It focuses on inculcating leadership qualities among students while sensitizing them towards important global issues.</p>
                    <p class="hidden-text-2">The Chitkara University MUNSOC has conducted 6 successful delegations in the past, all of which received an overwhelming response and widespread participation. This time it is back with yet another one of its kind event and one the biggest MUNs ever.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h2 style="font-weight: 600">ABOUT THE CHITKARA MUN :</h2>
                    <p>Chitkara University Model United Nations Society proudly announces the 7th edition of the International MUN and the first ever CHITKARA MUN AND CLIMATE CHANGE SUMMIT. </p>
                    <p>As we aim at leading the world towards a safer and sustainable path, with our arms wide open, we invite those who are motivated by the desire to achieve, the desire to make a change and the desire to be a step ahead to be a part of one of the finest conference ever.</p>
                    <p class="text-center show-more show-more-3" onclick="showMoreText('3')">Show more <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></p>
                    <p class="hidden-text-3">The delegation will be an amalgamation of 5 committees, each of which will be witness to intense deliberations and thought-provoking discussions. Also, we have the International Press which will be responsible for presenting the happenings of the event in an unbiased yet quirky way. </p>
                    <p class="hidden-text-3">The 3-day summit has been scheduled from 11-13 January, 2019 and will be held at Chitkara University, Rajpura (Punjab) Campus (India). </p>
